description:
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Title: Hospital Porter&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location/Trust: &lt;span&gt;Salford Royal NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Department: Estates &amp; Facilities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Band/Pay rate: £9.21(Enhanced rates for nights and weekends)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: Rota Basis- Over 24hrs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Placement Ref: 36666&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Role&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to be part of a team that works well together, always there to help each other? Would you like to work in a Trust that recently had outstanding in their CQC report? This location is easily accessible by public transport and has onsite parking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have answered yes, The Salford Royal Foundation Trust would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a temporary placement opportunity available for Porters at Salford Royal Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Staff will be providing the following support to the Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To move patients in and around the hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collecting the waste from wards and departments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The skills required are&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reliable, punctual, and flexible&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Able to work in a high-pressure environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Must be flexible as varied shift patterns.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be able to communicate effectively with colleagues&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Able to work part of a team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A good understanding of the Trust Values and behaviours and ability to demonstrate these values in the working day&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salford Royal is based at Stott Lane, and it is easily accessible via both car and public transport. There is onsite parking (fees will apply). It has four on site cafes and two restaurants where staff are eligible for a discount. The hospital also has on site shops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Staff who work at Salford Royal have said the following&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“It is a great environment to work in and has a good support network from managers”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your hard work commitment NHS Professionals (NHSP) can offer you some fantastic benefits: –&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Pay Rates &lt;/strong&gt;- work this week, get paid next week!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First choice of placements at over 50 NHS Trusts in England &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dedicated consultants&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible working options&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free DBS and free training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build holiday allowance &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support when you need it – 24/7 365 days&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder pension scheme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are NHS Professionals?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS Professionals (NHSP), owned by the Department of Health and Social Care (DHSC), works in partnership with hospital trusts to provide a bank of highly skilled temporary workers who want to work flexibly within the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working through the NHSP bank means Trusts don’t have to rely on expensive agencies. Right now, we have over 130,000 members registered on our bank from various roles, grades and specialities, saving the NHS over &lt;strong&gt;£70 million&lt;/strong&gt; each year. This money is then reinvested back into the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disclaimer &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note, you will be contacted by email throughout the recruitment process, so please check your emails, including your junk/spam regularly. We regret we cannot contact everyone who is not selected for an interview, therefore if you do not hear from us within 21 days after submitting your application, please assume you have not been successful on this occasion&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
